data.description: Exceptional 2-bed, 2-bath condo with luxurious features in every detail. Revel in hardwood floors, a contemporary kitchen with a gas stove, and expansive walk-in closets. The highlight is the rooftop patio, a true urban oasis, complete with a sauna, fire table, and outdoor grilling space. Accessible via a chic spiral staircase, this space is perfect for entertaining or enjoying city views. Elevate your living experience in this sophisticated condo with a perfect blend of style and comfort. Don't forget about the dog run for your furry companions!
